Steps to install flask on Centos6:
===================================
wget  wget http://mirror-fpt-telecom.fpt.net/fedora/epel/6/i386/epel-release-6-8.noarch.rpm
sudo rpm -ivh epel-release-6-8.noarch.rpm 
sudo yum install python-pip
sudo pip install flask


Work with the Flask book examples
================================

Install:

flask-script
flask-bootstrap
argparse
flask-wtf

